The evidence with the title 'Greg Abbott - Wikipedia ' says Gregory Wayne Abbott (born november 13, 1957) is an American lawyer and politician who has been the 48th governor of Texas since january 2015. A Republican, Abbott previously served as the 50th Attorney General Of Texas from 2002 to 2015. He is the first governor of any U.S. state since George Wallace to  ... At the beginning of junior high school, Abbott's family moved to Duncanville. 
